description: Eco-Tek Group, Inc. manufactures and distributes synthetic lubricants, filtration systems, and other products in North America. The company offers synthetic base motor oil, fuel treatment products, engine flush products, synthetic oil stabilizers, bypass and magnetic oil filtration products, hand cleaners, and non-toxic lubricants. Its products are used in cars, vans, sport utility vehicles, light trucks, heavy-duty industrial equipment, commercial and heavy transport vehicles, farm equipment, 4-cylinder lawn and garden equipment, compressors, and generators. The company markets and sells its products under the Eco-Tek brand name through independent sales agents and distributors, as well as through auto centers and oil change businesses. Eco-Tek Group, Inc. was founded in 2005 and is based in Woodbridge, Canada.
